-d1 "{{"1d8 [radiant]" if level < 14 else "2d8 [radiant]"}}" -f "Divine Strike|At 8th level, you gain the ability to infuse your weapon strikes with divine energy. Once on each of your turns when you hit a creature with a weapon attack, you can cause the attack to deal an extra 1d8 radiant damage to the target. When you reach 14th level, the extra damage increases to 2d8."